    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is an absolute gem and in pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! It's been totally pampered, garage-kept, and is basically flawless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
