      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, currently offered in showroom condition. This motorcar has been curated to the most exacting standards, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering an unrivaled opportunity for the discerning driver who demands excellence without compromise.",
