    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this car. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it basically looks and feels brand new! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it since day one, so there isn't a single blemish or scratch to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh interior smell. If you've been looking for a ride that's in truly perfect condition, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come see it\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
