    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The vehicle is mechanically superlative, with a documented Beisan Systems Vanos refresh and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from factory-spec bushings and a limited-slip differential that ensures optimal power delivery. With impeccable paint depth, zero curb rash on the Style 67 forged wheels, and a showroom-fresh interior, this M3 represents the pinnacle of analog driving dynamics.",
